  │  │  IMPLEMENTATION OPTIONS:                                            │   │
  │  │                                                                     │   │
  │  │  A) CSS 3D Transform (lightweight):                                 │   │
  │  │     • rotateX(60deg) for horizon tilt                               │   │
  │  │     • Animated translateZ() + sine-wave transform per row           │   │
  │  │     • Multiple parallax layers at different depths                  │   │
  │  │                                                                     │   │
  │  │  B) WebGL/Three.js (premium feel):                                  │   │
  │  │     • PlaneGeometry with vertex displacement                        │   │
  │  │     • Simplex noise for organic wave motion                         │   │
  │  │     • Fog for depth fade + perspective camera                       │   │
  │  │     • Instanced mesh for neural pattern                             │   │
  │  │                                                                     │   │
  │  │  WAVE CHARACTERISTICS:                                              │   │
  │  │     • 2-3 overlapping sine waves at different frequencies           │   │
  │  │     • Primary:   period ~25s, amplitude 60px                        │   │
  │  │     • Secondary: period ~17s, amplitude 30px, phase offset          │   │
  │  │     • Tertiary:  period ~11s, amplitude 15px (subtle ripple)        │   │
  │  │     • Creates organic, non-repeating motion                         │   │
  │  │                                                                     │   │
  │  │  DEPTH CUES:                                                        │   │
  │  │     • Nodes shrink toward horizon (perspective)                     │   │
  │  │     • Opacity fades from 0.06 (near) to 0.01 (far)                  │   │
  │  │     • Blur increases with distance (depth of field)                 │   │
  │  │     • Wave peaks appear brighter (catch light)                      │   │
  │  │                                                                     │   │
  │  │  LIGHTNING FLASHES: (unchanged)                                     │   │
  │  │     • Random regions bloom to ~0.4 opacity                          │   │
  │  │     • Color: #00d4ff with gaussian blur                             │   │
  │  │     • Flash follows wave geometry (illuminates 3D surface)          │   │
